ution.chiselled","http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/writing/lod/1",{"_":40,"ana":41},"Rubrication","#execution.rubrication",{"lettering":43,"dimensions":44},"Tall, slightly curved letters, mostly with minimal serifs. P is open; R is closed with long tail; E has short horizontals of equal length, slightly upward curving; M is four equal slanting strokes. In line 5 the O and C of 'procos' are intelinked, and the following O is small and mid-line. A large diagonal upward stroke is visible above the first letter of each of the civic ethnics; and a horizontal above the Q at the end of line 6. The letters all show traces of dark paint (modern?).",[45,53,59,64,70,75,79,84,90,95,97,101,105],{"type":46,"l":47,"from":48,"to":48,"h":49,"unit":50,"atLeast":51,"atMost":52},"letterHeight","Line 1","line1","65-71","mm","65","71",{"type":46,"l":54,"from":55,"to":55,"h":56,"unit":50,"atLeast":57,"atMost":58},"Line 2","line2","68-74","68","74",{"type":46,"l":60,"from":61,"to":61,"h":62,"unit":50,"atLeast":63,"atMost":58},"Line 3","line3","70-74","70",{"type":46,"l":65,"from":66,"to":66,"h":67,"unit":50,"atLeast":68,"atMost":69},"Line 4","line4","72-75","72","75",{"type":46,"l":71,"from":72,"to":72,"h":73,"unit":50,"atLeast":74,"atMost":68},"Line 5","line5","67-72","67",{"type":46,"l":76,"from":77,"to":77,"h":78,"unit":50,"atLeast":74,"atMost":58},"Line 6","line6","67-74",{"type":46,"l":80,"from":81,"to":81,"h":82,"unit":50,"atLeast":58,"atMost":83},"Line 7","line7","74-78","78",{"type":85,"l":86,"from":48,"to":55,"h":87,"unit":50,"atLeast":88,"atMost":89},"interlinear","Interlineation line 1 to 2","50-52","50","52",{"type":85,"l":91,"from":55,"to":61,"h":92,"unit":50,"atLeast":93,"atMost":94},"Interlineation line 2 to 3","47-51","47","51",{"type":85,"l":96,"from":61,"to":66,"h":87,"unit":50,"atLeast":88,"atMost":89},"Interlineation line 3 to 4",{"type":85,"l":98,"from":66,"to":72,"h":99,"unit":50,"atLeast":88,"atMost":100},"Interlineation line 4 to 5","50-53","53",{"type":85,"l":102,"f